item.description: Contact Information Link to heading Office: (1) A.C. Meyers Vaenge 15, Room 2.095, Copenhagen, Denmark; (2) Selma Lagerlofs Vej 300, Room 3-2-05, Aalborg, Denmark Email: (1) tungkvt[at]cs[dot]aau[dot]dk; (2) kvttung[at]gmail[dot]com Biography Link to heading I am an Assistant Professor in the Department of Computer Science at Aalborg University. I am a faculty member in Center for Data-Intensive Systems. I am also affiliated with the department’s team on Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning and the university’s Center on AI for the People.
